  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for storm-kit",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for storm-kit fixes the following issues:\n\n- Remove JndiLookup from log4j 2.x jars during build to\n  prevent 'log4shell' code injection. (bsc#1193641, bsc#1193611, CVE-2021-44228)\n- Remove JMSAppender from log4j 1.2.x jars during build to prevent attacks when JMS is enabled (bsc#1193641, bsc#1193662, CVE-2021-4104)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
